text.tspan: Share of women in the workforce
Proportion of the female population aged 15+ that is economically active.
Data source: Our World In Data based on OECD (2017) and Long (1958)
Note: For some observations prior to 1960, the participation rate is calculated with respect to the female population aged 14+.
